Risks Related to Senti and the shares of our common stock
The Senti stock price is volatile, and you could lose part of all of your investment.
Similar to the trading prices of the common stock of other biotechnology companies, the trading price of our common stock is subject to wide fluctuations
in response to various factors, some of which are beyond our control, including limited trading volume. The market price for our shares of our Common Stock
may be influenced by many factors, including the other risks described in this section of the Annual Report entitled “Risk Factors” and the following:
•
